item.title: 300 Swings Challenge
item.description: I have just finished the 300 swings a day for 30 days kettlebell challenge. It is a straightforward enough challenge; do 300 swings a day with one or two arms for 30 days. Men should use a 24kg bell and women 16kg. You can do the 300 in any combination of reps and sets throughout the day. I have been working out with kettlebells fairly consistently, 2-4 sessions a week, for the last six months.
